<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="178" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[140,1108,1222,1425]" pageId="3" pageNumber="178">
The following key was modified from 
<bibRefCitation author="Haghebaert G" box="[564,784,1222,1249]" pageId="3" pageNumber="178" pagination="223 - 234" refId="ref4436" refString="Haghebaert G (1991) A review of the Diglotta of the world (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Aleocharinae). Bulletin et Annales de la Societe Royale Belge d'Entomologie 127: 223 - 234." type="journal article" year="1991">Haghebaert (1991)</bibRefCitation>
. Elytral length was measured from the humeral angle to the hind margin; body length was measured from the apical margin of the labrum to the apex of the abdomen. Th e body length is given without range for species known only from a 
<typeStatus box="[547,646,1328,1354]" pageId="3" pageNumber="178">holotype</typeStatus>
(
<taxonomicName box="[662,786,1328,1354]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Diglotta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="178" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="littoralis">
<emphasis box="[662,786,1328,1354]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="178">D. littoralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), or where such data was not available from the literature. For descriptions and genital illustrations of 
<taxonomicName box="[956,1064,1363,1389]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Diglotta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="178" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="legneri">
<emphasis box="[956,1064,1363,1389]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="178">D. legneri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Diglotta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="178" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="littoralis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="178">D. littoralis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fenyes" authorityYear="1921" box="[286,404,1399,1425]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Diglotta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="178" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pacifica">
<emphasis box="[286,404,1399,1425]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="178">D. pacifica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
see 
<bibRefCitation author="Haghebaert G" box="[451,672,1398,1425]" pageId="3" pageNumber="178" pagination="223 - 234" refId="ref4436" refString="Haghebaert G (1991) A review of the Diglotta of the world (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Aleocharinae). Bulletin et Annales de la Societe Royale Belge d'Entomologie 127: 223 - 234." type="journal article" year="1991">Haghebaert (1991)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
